title: Fiona
body:
<<if visited ("Fiona") is false>>
Norra: Hey Fiona!
<<if visited ("Tim") is true>>
Norra: Tim said you needed some help with the budgies.
Fiona: Definitely. Can you help now?
[[Yeah, what can I do? |Fiona.Help]]
[[Not right now, sorry. |Fiona.Exit]]
<<else>>
Fiona: Hi, Norra. 
Fiona: I could use your help here. Do you have a minute?
[[Yeah, what can I do? |Fiona.Help]]
[[Not right now, sorry. |Fiona.Exit]]
<<endif>>
<<else>>
Fiona: Hi, Norra. 
Fiona: Can you help me now?
[[Yeah, what can I do? |Fiona.Help]]
[[Not right now, sorry. |Fiona.Exit]]
<<endif>>

title: Fiona.Help
body:
Fiona: We have to feed the budgies.
Fiona: I am cutting up some fruit and veg for them now. 
Fiona: I forgot the keys to the aviary up at the toolshed. Can you grab them?
Fiona: While you're up there, can you grab the birdseed?
Fiona: The bucket is too heavy for me to carry. 
<<set $received_supply_list_from_Fiona to true>>
[[No problem! |Fiona.Exit2]]
[[I can't right now, sorry. |Fiona.Exit]]

title: Fiona.Exit
body: Fiona: Okay, come back when you have some time.
